						               													<description>Scorpion Supreme is dead and the Subcommanders in the Scorp Corps are staking their claim to the title.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Ruthless 86, you take on the role of a brash, outrageous 80s cartoon villain, like steampunk pirate Molly Roger, the enigmatic and unknowable Sylence, or Tyrannoczar, a super soldier cloned from the DNA of history&amp;rsquo;s greatest rulers plus a T-Rex. &amp;#10; Prove to your rivals that you deserve to inherit the Scorpion Supreme title from your mysteriously departed leader. Win the loyalty of a legion of disposable Scorpion Soldiers and send them on Missions around the World. Expand and fortify your HexQuarters, your remote lair. Commandeer your evil organization&amp;rsquo;s Doomsday Devices. Stab backs, 86 your enemies, and, most of all, get Ruthless.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Ruthless 86 is a dice builder worker placement game. Recruit and deploy Troopers to battle stations in your remote HexQuarters, or combine six on a die to form a unit and deploy them on Missions across the World. Successful Missions expand your reach and Fortify your HexQuarters. When you feel you've built up a strong enough army, deploy to The Ranks and attempt to be the first to rise to the top and become the new Scorpion Supreme.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
